{"lemma":"فَراشاتٌ","slug":"فَراشاتٌ","root":"ف.ر.ش","root_slug":"ف-ر-ش","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ر-ش","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33535"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B4%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"butterfly","tags":["singulative"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Singular of فَرَاش (farāš)."},"ipa":["/fa.raː.ʃa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33535","headword_ar":"فَرَاشَةٌ","root":"fr$","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraA$N","text_ar":"فَرَاشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in ten places.       -A2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small quantity of water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, K, TA:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lamo yaboqa fiY AlA_inaA='i A_il~aA faraA$apN","text_ar":"لَمْ يَبْقَ فِى الاـِنَا=ءِ اـِلَّا فَرَاشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There remained not in the vessel save a small quantity of water"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small quantity of water remaining in pools left by torrents, the ground beneath which is seen, by reason of its clearness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place where water collects and remains in a smooth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard and smooth, rock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Great stones, like mill-stones, which are laid first"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a foundation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and upon which is then built a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarokiyb","text_ar":"تَرْكِيب"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an enclosure for palm-trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfaraA$ataAni","text_ar":"الفَرَاشَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Two cartilages near,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahaAp","text_ar":"لَهَاة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which generally means the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uvula;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but also, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arches,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pillars, of the soft palate;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"furthest part of the mouth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["A","O","K","TA"]}]}}